name: Ninepoint Crypto and AI Leaders ETF
longDescription: The Web3 ETF seeks to provide Unitholders with capital appreciation by investing in a diversified portfolio comprised primarily of equity and equity-related securities of companies that give investors exposure to emerging technologies such as Web3, the blockchain and digital asset-enabled internet.
